ACE WIEJSKIE W MA\u0141OPOLSCE I NA PODKARPACIU\n | trans-title = RURAL HOUSES AND PALACES IN LESSER POLAND AND SUBCARPATHIA\n | year = 2012\n | website = dworyipalace.com.pl\n | location = [[Pozna\u0144]], [[Poland|POLAND]], EU\n | publisher = Dom Wydawniczy Rebis\n | format = website\n | url = http://dworyipalace.com.pl/dwory-i-palace-michalowice.html\n | language = Polish\n | type = Online excerpt from printed book\n | accessdate = 17 August 2018\n | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170829202613/http://dworyipalace.com.pl/dwory-i-palace-michalowice.html\n | archivedate = 29 August 2017\n | quote = ''Nietrudno w tym konglomeracie bry\u0142, historycznych form i dekoracji z\u0142o\u017conych w intryguj\u0105c\u0105 i harmonijn\u0105 ca\u0142o\u015b\u0107 odczyta\u0107 dzie\u0142o najoryginalniejszego krakowskiego architekta prze\u0142omu XIX i XX wieku, przedstawiciela romantycznego historyzmu, autora s\u0142ynnej serii kamienic przy ulicy Retoryka w Krakowie: Festina lente, D\u0142ugo my\u015bl \u2013 pr\u0119dko czy\u0144, Pod Os\u0142em, Pod \u015apiewaj\u0105c\u0105 \u017bab\u0105 Teodora Talowskiego (1857\u20131910).''}}</ref> and reminiscent of a suburban [[villa]], was constructed in the years 1892-1897, for the [[Szlachta|noble (szlachta)]] family, \u017b\u0105d\u0142o-D\u0105browski z D\u0105br\u00f3wki herbu (coat of arms) [[Radwan coat of arms|Radwan]]<ref>{{cite web\n   | url = https://image.slidesharecdn.com/mikmichalowickilite2-161212085641/95/dwr-dbrowskich-w-michaowicach-nowe-ycie-dworu-wystawa-4-1024.jpg?cb=1481533068\n   | title = DW\u00d3R D\u0104BROWSKICH W MICHA\u0141OWICACH - \"Nowe \u017cycie dworu\" (wystawa)\n   | date = 12 December 2016\n   | publisher = [[Ma\u0142opolska Institute of Culture]]\n   | location = [[Krak\u00f3w]], [[Krak\u00f3w County|Krak\u00f3w county]], [[Lesser Poland Voivodeship|Lesser Poland voivodeship]], Southern Poland, POLAND\n   | work = [[SlideShare]]\n   | accessdate = 3 June 2017\n   | archiveurl = htt