te otoczenie budowli by\u0142 popularny i ceniony w ostatniej dekadzie XIX wieku architekt, Teodor Talowski. (The eminent and respected designer, Teodor Talowski, was the architect of the structure, perfectly integrated in its hilly surroundings.)\n }}</ref><ref name=\"kwasniewska-talowski-wood\">{{cite journal\n   | last = Kwa\u015bniewska\n   | first = El\u017cbieta\n   | editor-last = Kwa\u015bniewska\n   | editor-first = El\u017cbieta\n   | year = 2010\n   | title = Matka Ma\u0142gorzata D\u0105browska z micha\u0142owickiego dworu\n   | trans-title = Mother Ma\u0142gorzata D\u0105browska From the Micha\u0142\u00f3w Manor\n   | journal = KWARTALNIK SPO\u0141ECZNO-KULTURALNY (SOCIAL AND CULTURAL QUARTERLY)\n   | volume = 1-2\n   | issue = 25-26\n   | page = 10\n   | issn = 1733-5507\n   | location = Micha\u0142owice, Krak\u00f3w county, Lesser Poland Voivodeship, POLAND, EU\n   | publisher = Stowarzyszenie Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Ziemi Micha\u0142owickiej \u201eNad D\u0142ubni\u0105\u201d\n   | language = Polish\n   | type = Journal, magazine: Periodical\n   | format = PDF\n   | url = https://www.michalowice.malopolska.pl/spzm/publikacje/nr25_26.pdf\n   | accessdate = 17 August 2018\n   | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180813054316/https://www.michalowice.malopolska.pl/spzm/publikacje/nr25_26.pdf\n   | archivedate = 13 August 2018  \n   | quote = Dworek \u201ekollatajowski\u201d \u2013 miejsce urodzin Matki Malgorzaty, dw\u00f3r Dabrowskich proj. T. Talowskiego i \u00f3wczesny park wok\u00f3l dworu w Michalowicach}}</ref><ref>{{cite web\n | last = Libicki\n | first = Piotr\n | title = DWORY I PA\u0141ACE WIEJSKIE W MA\u0141OPOLSCE I NA PODKARPACIU\n | trans-title = RURAL HOUSES AND PALACES IN LESSER POLAND AND SUBCARPATHIA\n | year = 2012\n | website = dworyipalace.com.pl\n | location = [[Pozna\u0144]], [[Poland|POLAND]], EU\n | publisher = Dom Wydawniczy Rebis\n | format = website\n | url = http://dworyipalace.com.pl/dwory-i-palace-michalowice.html\n | l